(123, 3, 1, 'Unsparing judgment, in that dark, lone hour,'),
(123, 3, 2, 'In love He bore;'),
(123, 3, 3, 'Laid down His life, destroyed death''s fearful power;'),
(123, 3, 4, 'His work is o''er!'),
(123, 3, 5, 'Atonement made, God fully satisfied,'),
(123, 3, 6, 'The mighty Saviour''s ris''n and glorified.'),
(123, 4, 1, 'God''s secret things, long treasured up in heav''n,'),
