(127, 2, 3, 'In that love for ever living -'),
(127, 2, 4, 'Love, all thought above.'),
(127, 3, 1, 'And we know that Thou wouldst have us'),
(127, 3, 2, 'Ever dwell with Thee:'),
(127, 3, 3, 'Now to live in love unbounded,'),
(127, 3, 4, 'And eternally.'),
(127, 4, 1, 'Hold our hearts, O Lord, we pray Thee,'),
(127, 4, 2, 'By and in Thy love,'),
(127, 4, 3, 'Till we dwell with Thee in glory'),
(127, 4, 4, 'Evermore above.'),
(128, 1, 1, 'Our God, we bless Thee, glorious source'),
(128, 1, 2, 'Of light and love divine;'),
(128, 1, 3, 'From Thee all blessing emanates,'),
(128, 1, 4, 'The power, the greatness Thine;'),
(128, 1, 5, 'Both heav''n and earth belong to Thee,'),
(128, 1, 6, 'We joy in Thy supremacy.'),
(128, 2, 1, 'Exalted, Thou, as Head o''er all;'),
(128, 2, 2, 'Majestic is Thy seat!'),
(128, 2, 3, 'Thy glorious Name our souls revere,'),
(128, 2, 4, 'And worship, as is meet.'),
(128, 2, 5, 'Complacent Thou in love, we see'),
(128, 2, 6, 'All things made subject unto Thee.'),
(128, 3, 1, 'We thus anticipate Thy day,'),
