(133, 3, 4, 'And through righteousness now reigns.'),
(133, 3, 5, 'Here the Spirit too bears witness'),
(133, 3, 6, 'To the truth that all is done.'),
(133, 3, 7, 'O the wonder of the moment -'),
(133, 3, 8, 'God outshining in His Son!'),
(134, 1, 1, 'We sing to Thee, Lord Jesus,'),
