(301, 2, 2, 'Of myriads sanctified'),
(301, 2, 3, 'All merge in perfect oneness,'),
(301, 2, 4, 'Responding as Thy bride.'),
(301, 3, 1, 'This joy Thou long hast waited,'),
(301, 3, 2, 'But now with raptured gaze'),
